values: It has been a long time since I made an entry. Every time I open my favorite links, live journal stares me in the face, but I just pass by. Today was the day to click on the link. Since my last entry lots has happened but too much to type, but perhaps I will keep adding entries. hello live journal, i missed ya!
It has been 31 weeks since my last entry. It has been so very long. Really all I have to say anyhow is tomorrrow morning I will be on my first flight to my first visit to New York City.
This is now a personal journal for my eyes and friends only.
